Subject:[CT Birds] geese flying at night
Paul,
I do indeed occasionally hear the Canada  Geese flying at night.  The eeriest time was on January 20 2001 in New Jersey a few hours before my father died.  I felt they were carrying his spirit away.

Susanne Shrader
birdgirrl@comcast.net




